title: Fellow Daoist, Your Script Is So Beautiful

Description :
        Fellow Daoist, your script is so beautifulFellow Daoist, your script is so beautifulBeing able to see other people's life scripts, I thought it would be an explosive start, but I never thought the system would want to kill me! The pure lu** master sister, the enchanting beast girl, the ascetic saint  each intends to kill me~
